originalText.text: God is Love, you feel the love here, his presence. The congregation is warm, kind, wonderful and so welcoming. The pastors, everyone is just great. I've been a member for 10 yrs plus.

originalText.text:
Rev Vicente & Delia Ortiz
Were the founder of El Taberculo De La Fe
They started in 46 Hamilton Place then as the congregation started to grow they move to the old RKO & Casino property, finally they were able to purchase this property.
Many have come and gone to different part of the world as Missionary, Evangelist, Pastors...
Pastors Vicente and Delia were special people they gave their life here in the City of New York.
It was a challenging ministry when they were full Gospel Ministers but they over came those obstacles. The had 5 children's as they were in the full ministry.
There names are Vilma, Mildred, Dorcas, Rebecca, Vincent. Rev Vicente Ortiz pass to be with his Saviour his wife Delia just turn 93 year old lives somewhere in Florida.
There children are all over the u.s.a.they are faithful to the Lord in the different places.
